Feature 1: User Authentication + Profile User Stories:
“As a new user, I want to create an account so that I can save my information.”

“As a returning user, I want to log in so I can access my profile and shoe results.”

“As a user, I want to fill out my profile (height, weight, gender, age, activity level) so that the app can personalize shoe recommendations.”

“As a user, I want to log out securely when I’m done using the app.”

“As a user, I want my personal information to be stored securely to protect my privacy.”

“As a user, I want to ask the AI bot questions if I need help navigating or understanding shoe recommendations.”
Feature 2: Foot Scanner & Gait Analysis + Extras
“As a user, I want to scan my foot using my phone’s camera so that the app can measure its size and shape.”

“As a user, I want to record a short video of the way I walk so that the app can analyze my gait.”

“As a user, I want to upload existing photos or videos of my foot or walk in case I can’t scan live.”

“As a user, I want clear instructions on how to perform the scan and video to ensure accurate results.”

“As a user, I want feedback after the scan/video confirming the process was successful or asking me to try again if needed.”

“As a user, I want to know my arch type (low, medium, high), foot width, and narrowness level from the scan results.”

“As a user, I want to filter shoe recommendations by brand, color, activity type, size, and other preferences.”

👟 Feature 3: Smart Shoe Recommendations
“As a user, I want to receive personalized shoe recommendations based on my foot scan and profile data so that I can find shoes that fit well.”

“As a user, I want recommendations to be categorized by activity type (running, football, standing, casual, etc.) so I can easily find shoes for my needs.”

“As a user, I want to see detailed information about each recommended shoe, including brand, price, and user reviews.”

“As a user, I want to save my favorite shoes to a wishlist or favorites list.”

“As a user, I want the app to update recommendations if I change my profile data or activity preferences.”

“As a user, I want to filter or sort recommendations by price, brand, or rating.”
